  "name": "Secret Source Automaton: Hunter-Seeker",
  "desc": "An ancient ruin automaton used in object collection.<br>Legend has it that these ancient ruin machines were designed for specialized work functions, primarily conducting experimental work such as capturing and collecting samples, and had only basic combat functionality.<br>According to rumor, these were not built by humans, but are instead creations of a yet more ancient civilization. Today, that civilization has been lost, and all that remains are these strange machines that roam the land.",
